quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  38,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  38,1,"s, qasam hai nasiyaat bharay quran ki"
  38,2,"balkay yahi log, jinhon ne maan-ne se inkaar kya hai, sakht taqqabur aur zid mein mubtala hain"
  38,3,"inn se pehlay hum aisi kitni hi qomon ko halaak kar chuke hain ( aur jab unn ki shamat aayi hai ) to woh cheekh utthay hain, magar woh waqt bachney ka nahi hota"
  38,4,"inn logon ko is baat par bara taajjub howa ke aik darane wala khud aِnhi mein se agaya munkareen kehnay lagey ke"" yeh sahit hai, sakht jhoota hai"
  38,5,"kya iss ne saaray khudaon ki jagah bas aik hi khuda bana dala? yeh to barri ajeeb baat hai """
  38,6,"aur sardaran -e- qoum yeh kehte hue nikal gay ke"" chalo aur datay raho apne mabodon ki ibadat par yeh baat to kisi aur hi gharz se kahi ja rahi hai"
  38,7,yeh baat hum ne zamana qareeb ki millat mein kisi se nahi suni yeh kuch nahi hai magar aik mann gharat baat
  38,8,"kya hamaray darmain bas yahishakhs reh gaya tha jis par Allah ka zikar nazil kar diya gaya ?"" asal baat yeh hai ke yeh mere"" zikar"" par shak kar rahay hain, aur yeh saari baatein is liye kar rahay hain ke unhon ne mere azaab ka maza chakkha nahi hai"
  38,9,kya tairay dataa aur ghalib parvar-digaar ki rehmat ke khazanay inn ke qabzay mein hain ?
  38,10,kya yeh aasman o zameen aur un ke darmain ki cheezon ke maalik hain? acha to yeh aalam asbaab ki bulandiyon par charh kar dekhen !
  38,11,yeh to jathonmein se aik chhota sa jatha hai jo isi jagah shikast khanay wala hai
  38,12,"inn se pehlay Nooh ki qoum, aur Aad , aur mekhon wala firaon"
  38,13,"aur smod, aur qoum Loot , aur aikah walay jhutla chuke hain jthe woh thay"
  38,14,un mein se har aik ne Rasolo-n ko jhtlaya aur meri uqobat ka faisla is par chaspan ho kar raha
  38,15,yeh log bhi bas aik dhamakay ke muntazir hain jis ke baad koi dosra dhamaka nah hoga
  38,16,"aur yeh kehte hain ke ae hamaray rab, yom ul hisaab se pehlay hi hamara hissa hamein jaldi se de day"
  38,17,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, sabr karo unn baton par jo yeh log banatay hain, aur inn ke samnay hamaray bande DAWOD ka qissa bayan karo jo barri quwatoon ka maalik tha har maamla mein Allah ki taraf rujoo karne wala tha"
  38,18,hum ne pahoron ko is ke sath maskhar kar rakha tha ke subah o shaam woh is ke sath tasbeeh karte thay
  38,19,parinday simat atay aur sab ke sab uss ki tasbeeh ki taraf mutwajjah ho jatay thay
  38,20,"hum ne is ki saltanat mazboot kar di thay, is ko hikmat ataa ki thay aur faisla kin baat kehnay ki salahiyat bakhsh thi"
  38,21,phir tumhe kuch khabar pohanchi hai unn muqadmay walon ki jo deewar charh kar uss ke baala khanaay mein ghis aeye thay ?
  38,22,"jab woh DAWOD ke paas puhanche to woh inhen dekh kar ghabra gaya unhon ne kaha"" daryay nahi, hum do fareeq muqadma hain jin mein se aik ne dosray par zayad-ti ki hai aap hamaray darmain theek theek haq ke sath faisla kar degiye, be insafi nah kiijiye aur hamein raah raast bataiye"
  38,23,"yeh mera bhai hai, iss ke paas ninanway dunbiyan hain aur mere paas sirf aik hi dunbi hai iss ne mujh se kaha ke yeh aik dunbi bhi mere hawalay kar day aur is ne guftagu mein mujhe daba liya """
  38,24,"DAWOD ne jawab diya :"" iss shakhs ne apni dunbiyon ke sath teri dunbi mila lainay ka mutalba kar ke yaqeenan tujh par zulm kya, aur waqea yeh hai ke mil jal kar sath rehne walay log aksar aik dosray par zyadtyan karte rehtay hain, bas wohi log is se bachay hue hain jo imaan rakhtay aur amal Saleh karte hain, aur aisay log kam hi hain"" ( yeh baat kehte kehte ) DAWOD samajh gaya ke yeh to hum ne darasal is ki azmaish ki hai, chunancha is ne apne rab se maffi mangi aur sjday mein gir gaya aur rujoo kar liya"
  38,25,tab hum ne is ka woh qasoor maaf kya aur yaqeenan hamaray haan is ke liye taqarab ka maqam aur behtar injaam hai
  38,26,"( hum ne is se kaha )"" ae DAWOD, hum ne tujhe zameen mein khalifa banaya hai, lehaza to logon ke darmain haq ke sath hukoomat kar aur khwahish nafs ki pairwi nah kar ke woh tujhe Allah ki raah se bhatka day gi jo log Allah ki raah se bhataktay hain yaqeenan unn ke liye sakht saza hai ke woh yom اul hisaab ko bhool gay """
  38,27,"hum ne is aasman aur zameen ko, aur is duniya ko jo un ke darmain hai, fuzool peda nahi kar diya hai yeh to unn logon ka gumaan hai jinhon ne kufar kya hai, aur aisay kafiroon ke liye barbadi hai jahannum ki aag se"
  38,28,kya hum unn logon ko jo imaan laatay hain aur naik aamaal karte hain aur unn ko jo zameen mein fasaad karne walay hain yaksaa kar den? kya Muttaqiyun ko hum fajron jaissa kar dein ?
  38,29,yeh aik barri barket wali kitaab hai jo ( aeMuhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam) hum ne tumhari taraf nazil ki hai taakay yeh log is ki ayaat par ghhor karen aur aqal o fikar rakhnay walay is se sabaq len
  38,30,"aur DAWOD ko hum ne sulaiman ( jaissa beta ) ataa kya, behtareen bandah, kasrat se apne rab ki taraf rujoo karne wala"
  38,31,qabil zikar hai woh mauqa jab shaam ke waqt is ke samnay khoob sodhayhue taiz ro ghoray paish kiye gay
  38,32,"to is ne kaha"" mein ne is maal ki mohabbat apne rab ki yaad ki wajah se ikhtiyar ki hai"" yahan taq ke jab woh ghoray nigah se oojhal ho gay"
  38,33,"to ( is ne hukum diya ke ) inhen mere paas wapas lao, phir laga un ki pindliyon aur gardnon par haath phairnay"
  38,34,aur ( dekho ke ) sulaiman ko bhi hum ne azmaish mein dala aur is ki kursi par aik jsd laa kar daal diya phir is ne rujoo kya
  38,35,"aur kaha ke"" ae mere rab, mujhe maaf kar day aur mujhe woh badshahi day jo mere baad kisi ke liye sazawar nah ho, bay shak to hi asal dataa hai """
  38,36,tab hum ne is ke liye howa ko maskhar kar diya jo is ke hukum se narmi ke sath chalti thi jidhar woh chahta tha
  38,37,"aur shyatin ko maskhar kar diya, har terhan ke maimaar aur ghouta Khor"
  38,38,aur dosray jo paband salasil thay
  38,39,"( hum ne uss se kaha )"" yeh hamari bakhshish hai, tujhe ikhtiyar hai jisay chahay day aur jis se chahay rok le, koi hisaab nahi """
  38,40,yaqeenan uss ke liye hamaray haan taqarab ka maqam aur behtar injaam hai
  38,41,"aur hamaray bande ayub ka zikar karo, jab is ne apne rab ko puraka ke shetan ne mujhe sakht takleef aur azaab mein daal diya hai"
  38,42,"( hum ne ussay hukum diya ) apna paon zameen par maar, yeh hai thanda pani nahanay ke liye aur peenay ke liye"
  38,43,"hum ne ussay is ke ahal o Ayal wapas diye aur un ke sath itnay hi aur, apni taraf se rehmat ke tor par, aur aqal o fikar rakhnay walon ke liye dars ke tor par"
  38,44,"( aur hum ne is se kaha ) tinkon ka aik muttha le aur uss se maar day, apni qasam nah toar hum ne ussay sabir paaya, behtareen bandah, apne rab ki taraf bohat rujoo karne wala"
  38,45,"aur hamaray bundon, ibrahim aur ishaq aur yaqoob ka zikar karo barri qowat amal rakhnay walay aur deedaa war log thay"
  38,46,"hum ne unn ko aik khalis sift ki bana par bargzida kya tha, aur woh daar akhirat ki yaad thi"
  38,47,yaqeenan hamaray haan un ka shumaar chuney hue naik ashkhaas mein hai
  38,48,"aur Ismael aur alyus'a ا aur ZULKAFFAL ka zikar karo, yeh sab naik logon mein se thay"
  38,49,yeh aik zikar tha ( ab suno ke ) mut-taqi logon ke liye yaqeenan behtareen thikana hai
  38,50,hamesha rehne wali jannaten jin ke darwazay unn ke liye khulay hon ge
  38,51,"un mein woh takiye lagaye baithy hon ge, khoob khoob fawaka aur mashrobat talab kar rahay hon ge"
  38,52,aur un ke paas Sharmeeli hum sun biwiyan hon gi
  38,53,yeh woh cheeze hain jinhein hisaab ke din ataa karne ka tum se wada kya ja raha hai
  38,54,yeh hamara rizaq hai jo kabhi khatam honay wala nahi
  38,55,yeh to hai Muttaqiyun ka injaam aur sarkashon ke liye bad tareen thikana hai
  38,56,"jahannum jis mein woh jhulsa-ay jayen ge, bohat hi buri qiyam gaah"
  38,57,"yeh hai unn ke liye, pas woh maza chakhain kholtey hue pani aur peep lahoo"
  38,58,aur isi qisam ki doosri talkhyon ka
  38,59,"( woh jahannum ki taraf apne pairwon (manay walay(ko atay dekh kar aapas mein kahin ge )"" yeh aik lashkar tumahray paas ghisa chala aa raha hai, koi khush aamdeed inn ke liye nahi hai, yeh aag mein jhlsne walay hain """
  38,60,"woh unn ko jawab den ge"" nahi balkay tum hi jhulsay ja rahay ho, koi kher muqaddam tumahray liye nahi tum hi to yeh injaam hamaray agay laaye ho, kaisi buri hai yeh jaye qarar """
  38,61,"phir woh kahin ge"" ae hamaray rab, jis ne hamein is injaam ko pohanchanay ka bandobast kya uss ko dozakh ka dohra azaab day """
  38,62,"aur woh aapas mein kahin ge"" kya baat hai, hum unn logon ko kahin nahi dekhte jinhein hum duniya mein bura samajte thay ?"
  38,63,"hum ne yuhin un ka mazaq bana liya tha, ya woh kahin nazron se oojhal hain? """
  38,64,"be shak yeh baat sachhi hai, ahal dozakh mein yahi kuch jhagrre honay walay hain"
  38,65,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) inn se kaho,"" mein to bas khabardaar kar dainay wala hon koi haqeeqi mabood nahi magar Allah , jo yaktaa hai, sab par ghalib"
  38,66,"asmano aur zameen ka maalik aur unn saari cheezon ka maalik jo un ke darmain hain, zabardast aur dar guzar karne wala """
  38,67,"inn se kaho"" yeh aik barri khabar hai"
  38,68,"jis ko sun kar tum mun phertey ho """
  38,69,"( un se kaho )"" mujhe uss waqt ki koi khabar nah thi jab mal-ayaala mein jhagra ho raha tha"
  38,70,"mujh ko to wahi ke zareya se yeh baatein sirf is liye batayi jati hain ke mein khula khula khabardaar karne wala hon """
  38,71,"jab tairay rab ne firshton se kaha"" mein matti se aik bashar bananay wala hon"
  38,72,"phir jab mein usay poori terhan bana dun aur is mein apni rooh phoonk dun to tum is ke agay sjday mein gir jao """
  38,73,is hukum ke mutabiq farishtay sab ke sab sjday mein gir gay
  38,74,magar iblees ne apni barayi ka ghamand kya aur woh kafiroon mein se ho gaya
  38,75,"rab ne farmaya"" ae iblees, tujhe kya cheez uss ko sajda karne se Maney hui jisay mein ne apne dono hathon se banaya hai? to bara ban raha hai ya to hai hi kuch ounchay darjay ki hstyon mein se? """
  38,76,"uss ne jawab diya"" mein uss se behtar hon, aap ne mujh ko aag se peda kya hai aur is ko matti se """
  38,77,"farmaya"" acha to yahan se nikal ja, to mardood hai"
  38,78,"aur tairay oopar yom ul jaza taq meri laanat hai """
  38,79,"woh bola"" a y mere rab, yeh baat hai to phir mujhe uss waqt taq ke liye mohlat day day jab yeh log dobarah uthaye jayen ge """
  38,80,"farmaya,"" acha, tujhe uss roz taq ki mohlat hai"
  38,81,"jis ka waqt mujhe maloom hai """
  38,82,"is ne kaha"" teri izzat ki qasam, mein inn sab logo n ko b_hka kar rahon ga"
  38,83,"bajuz tairay unn bundon ke jinhein to ne khalis kar liya hai """
  38,84,"farmaya"" to haq yeh hai, aur mein haq hi kaha karta hon"
  38,85,"ke mein jahannum ko tujh se aur unn sab logon se bhar dun ga jo inn insanon mein se teri pairwi karen ge """
  38,86,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) inn se keh do ke mein is tableegh par tum se koi ajar nahi maangta, aur nah mein banawati logon mein se hon"
  38,87,yeh to aik nasiyaat hai tamam Jahan walon ke liye
  38,88,aur thori muddat hi guzray gi ke tumhe is ka haal khud maloom ho jaye ga
